CREATE TABLE `bigquery-public-data.covid19_jhu_csse.summary`
(
  province_state STRING,
  country_region STRING,
  date DATE,
  latitude FLOAT64,
  longitude FLOAT64,
  location_geom GEOGRAPHY,
  confirmed INT64,
  deaths INT64,
  recovered STRING,
  active INT64,
  fips STRING,
  admin2 STRING,
  combined_key STRING
)
OPTIONS(
  description="Summary COVID-19 cases, aggregated by country/region and province/state. See the original source files here: https://github.com/CSSEGISandData/COVID-19/blob/master/csse_covid_19_data/csse_covid_19_time_series/",
  labels=[("freebqcovid", "")]
);
